tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE proteins (
  protein_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  protein_name VARCHAR(255),
  gene_name VARCHAR(255),
  molecular_weight DECIMAL(10,2),
  expression_level DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE datasets (
  dataset_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  dataset_name VARCHAR(255),
  source VARCHAR(255),
  date_uploaded TIMESTAMP,
  number_of_samples INT
);

CREATE TABLE analysis_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    sample_id INT NOT NULL,
    protein_id INT NOT NULL,
    result_value FLOAT NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (sample_id) REFERENCES samples(sample_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (protein_id) REFERENCES proteins(protein_id)
);

CREATE TABLE analysis_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    sample_id INT,
    protein_id INT,
    expression_level FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (sample_id) REFERENCES samples(sample_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (protein_id) REFERENCES proteins(id)
);

CREATE TABLE proteins (
	protein_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	protein_name VARCHAR(255),
	protein_sequence TEXT,
	molecular_weight DECIMAL,
	expression_level DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE experiments (
	experiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	experiment_date DATE,
	experiment_type VARCHAR(50),
	num_samples INT,
	researcher_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE analysis_results (
	result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	analysis_date DATE,
	result_text TEXT,
	protein_id INT,
	experiment_id INT
);
